response.description:
Dark Side of the Moon is an album like no other. For many, it's the highlight of Pink Floyd's illustrious career. Musically and lyrically, it stands as a cohesive piece of art: a reflection on the state of mankind in the modern world.

The Dark Side of the Moon project will look at how Pink Floyd explore these themes, one track at a time. Along the way, we'll learn about the people and technologies behind the album, and hear stories about its writing and recording. By the end, we'll have a deeper understanding of just why Dark Side of the Moon is such a magnificent piece of art.
